title: MS. MARVEL Vol 2 48-50 English - Fixed
description:
This wasn't really a request, but I noticed ShadowRadiance had attempted to post these yesterday and had tech problems. It occurred to me that I now knew about a site where I could find them to post.

Most of the first 47 issues are found in this torrent: http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/5274532/Ms._Marvel_Volume_2_Complete
And #37 was posted here: http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/5839739/Ms.Marvel_V2_redux

Ms. Marvel is Carol Danvers, the Avenger currently known as Captain Marvel.

Please seed and share.  --STF
